<!-- ════════════════ 03 · KERNSERVICES ════════════════ -->
  <section data-label="Kernservices" class="slide light">
    <div class="glow"></div>
    <div class="frame">
      <p class="eyebrow"><span class="num">02</span>Onze drie kernservices</p>
      <h1 class="title" style="max-width: 1600px;">Eerst inzicht, dan<br>de juiste <span class="accent">automatisatie</span>.</h1>

      <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top: 48px;">
        <div class="card svc" style="--c:#f59e0b">
          <div class="svc-head">
            <div class="svc-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="6" y1="3" x2="6" y2="15"/><circle cx="18" cy="6" r="3"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"/><path d="M18 9a9 9 0 0 1-9 9"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Procesoptimalisatie</h3>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size: 24px;">We brengen je proces volledig in kaart en zoeken waar de <strong>écht grote winst</strong> zit.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><span><strong>Volledige procesanalyse</strong>, geen giswerk</span></li>
            <li><span>Focus op de <strong>grootste hefbomen</strong></span></li>
            <li><span><strong>Echte impact</strong>, niet een paar procentjes</span></li>
            <li><span><strong>Doelen &amp; KPI's</strong> vooraf bepaald</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card svc" style="--c:#06b6d4">
          <div class="svc-head">
            <div class="svc-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="10" rx="2"/><circle cx="12" cy="5" r="2"/><path d="M12 7v4M8 15h.01M16 15h.01"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Agentic Automatisatie</h3>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size: 24px;">Niet alles hoeft een agent te zijn. <strong>Agents, workflows en code</strong> in harmonie.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><span><strong>ai agents</strong> die redeneren &amp; uitvoeren</span></li>
            <li><span><strong>Workflows en code</strong> waar dat beter past</span></li>
            <li><span>De <strong>juiste tool</strong> voor elke taak</span></li>
            <li><span><strong>Mens-in-de-loop</strong> controle</span></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="ss-tease">
            <span class="ss-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="1.5"/><circle cx="20" cy="4" r="1.5"/><circle cx="4" cy="20" r="1.5"/><circle cx="20" cy="20" r="1.5"/><line x1="5.4" y1="5.4" x2="9.9" y2="9.9"/><line x1="18.6" y1="5.4" x2="14.1" y2="9.9"/><line x1="5.4" y1="18.6" x2="9.9" y2="14.1"/><line x1="18.6" y1="18.6" x2="14.1" y2="14.1"/></svg></span>
            <span class="ss-txt">Aangedreven door <strong>SmartSpace</strong>, ons eigen agent-platform.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card svc" style="--c:#8b5cf6">
          <div class="svc-head">
            <div class="svc-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"/><path d="M6 12v5c3 3 9 3 12 0v-5"/></svg></div>
            <h3>Training &amp; Workshops</h3>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size: 24px;">Je mensen klaar voor de ai-era, inclusief onze <strong>eigen software</strong>.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><span>Op maat voor <strong>elk niveau</strong></span></li>
            <li><span><strong>Praktische ai-vaardigheden</strong></span></li>
            <li><span><strong>Onze eigen software</strong> uitgelegd, zodat iedereen mee is</span></li>
            <li><span><strong>Change-management</strong> &amp; adoptie</span></li>
          </ul>
